    {
      "date": "20.12.23",
      "version": "4.0.0",
      "changelog": [
        {
          "type": "breaking_changes",
          "changes": [
            "The modal is now created using a portal. It will be placed at the top level of the DOM. This may help with some z-index related issues. The modal no longer exists in the DOM when it is not open.",
            "Renamed the prop <code>hasPadding</code> to <code>noPadding</code>, and inverted it."
          ],
          "fixes": [
            "Because the modal no longer is in the DOM at all times, if you have any components inside a slot, their lifecycle hooks (e.g. <code>ngOnInit</code>) may be called every time the component is shown and not just when mounted the first time.",
            "If you are using it, replace <code>hasPadding</code> with <code>noPadding</code> and invert it."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
